OL,3,CPolice inspector took unauthorised job
OL,4,Cat World Cup while on career break
OL,6,FA Greater Manchester Police inspector
OL,7,Faccepted a job to work at the 2022
OL,8,Ffootball World Cup without permission
OL,9,Fwhile on a career break, a misconduct
OL,10,Fhearing has been told.
OL,12,FIn June 2020, Tariq Butt asked for
OL,13,Ftime away from the force for childcare
OL,14,Freasons and to go travelling but he
OL,15,Ffailed to mention he already had an
OL,16,Foffer for a key role at the tournament
OL,17,Fin Qatar.
OL,19,FThree months later he started his new
OL,20,Fpost on Fifa's Safety & Security
OL,21,FOperations Committee.
