OL,3,CPolice inspector took unauthorised job
OL,4,Cat World Cup while on career break
OL,6,FA disciplinary hearing found the
OL,7,Fofficer had breached the standards of
OL,8,Fbehaviour for discreditable conduct,
OL,9,Fconfidentiality, honesty and integrity
OL,10,Fand orders and instructions, the
OL,11,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,12,F(IOPC) said.
OL,14,FHe was found to have committed gross
OL,15,Fmisconduct and would have been
OL,16,Fdismissed had he not already resigned,
OL,17,Fadded the watchdog.
OL,19,FMr Butt will also be placed on the
OL,20,Fpolice barred list.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
