OL,3,CPolice inspector took unauthorised job
OL,4,Cat World Cup while on career break
OL,6,FDuring the investigation directed by
OL,7,Fthe IOPC, the career break policy was
OL,8,Freviewed, which confirmed officers
OL,9,Fneeded to obtain the permission of the
OL,10,Fchief constable before undertaking
OL,11,Fpaid employment or a business interest
OL,12,Fwhile on a career break and no such
OL,13,Fpermission was granted.
OL,15,FA file was passed to the Crown
OL,16,FProsecution Service which later
OL,17,Fconfirmed it would not take the matter
OL,18,Fany further, added the IOPC.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
