OL,3,CPolice inspector took unauthorised job
OL,4,Cat World Cup while on career break
OL,6,FSteve Noonan, IOPC director of
OL,7,Foperations, said: "Former inspector
OL,8,FButt has shown a complete disregard
OL,9,Ffor the rules and acted dishonestly
OL,10,Ffor his own personal gain. In doing
OL,11,Fso, he let down his colleagues and
OL,12,Frisked seriously undermining public
OL,13,Fconfidence.
OL,15,F"To ensure that the public receive the
OL,16,Fbest possible service, and in order to
OL,17,Fprevent conflicts of interest, police
OL,18,Fofficers are subject to additional
OL,19,Frestrictions; needing permission
OL,20,Fbefore undertaking further paid
OL,21,Femployment or a business interest.
