OL,3,CPolice inspector took unauthorised job
OL,4,Cat World Cup while on career break
OL,6,F"Knowing that such a permission was
OL,7,Fnot in place, inspector Butt flouted
OL,8,Fthe rules while claiming to be on a
OL,9,Fcareer break."
OL,11,FButt had applied for a three-year
OL,12,Fcareer break from the force stating he
OL,13,Fwould not work and would be
OL,14,Ffinancially supported by his family,
OL,15,Fsaid Greater Manchester Police (GMP).
