OL,6,FDet Supt Steve Keeley, of GMP's Anti-
OL,7,FCorruption Unit, said: "It is clear
OL,8,Fthat the actions of Tariq Butt
OL,9,Fdemonstrated a complete disregard for
OL,10,Fthe values of honesty and trust that
OL,11,Fwe and the public rightly expect of
OL,12,Four officers.
OL,14,F"If we cannot trust his actions then
OL,15,Fwe certainly cannot expect the public
OL,16,Fto do so either."
